          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/c369b96fc6417e8fc2bb607e37297ad4_7868130961589657944.png",
                "key": "潜形隐曜弓",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "潜形隐曜弓"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，此角色的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">破局</span>层数+2</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/b0033b9dfbdff746cfb03c7b73792a34_786351061576064176.png",
                "key": "萦络纵命索",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "萦络纵命索"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">玄掷玲珑</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">玄掷玲珑</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色普通攻击后：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/f92e763ec4e356d65ffc75d9443b7d22_4783626141805267798.png",
                "key": "渊图玲珑骰",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "渊图玲珑骰"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">破局</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">破局</span></strong></p><p>此状态初始具有1层「破局」；重复附属时，叠加1层「破局」。「破局」最多可以叠加到3层。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>叠加1层「破局」。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附属角色普通攻击时：</span>如果「破局」已有2层，则消耗2层「破局」，使造成的物理伤害转换为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，并抓1张牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/9c5eb94adf31a35a1dcf456b08342b00_5423042722425020509.png",
                "key": "破局",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "破局"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span>]</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>我方对敌方出战角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_3213953321375529.png",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗一层<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p>可用次数耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/20/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5218483646939834447.png",
